\'utilisateur à aussi la possibilité de créer des collections de parcours afin de les regrouper.\r\n<h3>Audio</h3>\r\nLa particularité de Triplink est que vous pouvez visiter des lieux, tout en écoutant des musiques en rapport avec celui-ci et l\'application tient aussi compte du choix de musique que vous avez choisi.'),(330,98,'_functionality','field_661e3953a2fa0'),(331,98,'colors','#F09D5D,#1B1A20,#FFFFFF,#F3F3F3'),(332,98,'_colors','field_6626134621eff'),(333,98,'_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes','0'),(334,98,'_yoast_wpseo_wordproof_timestamp',''),(335,100,'_wp_attached_file','2024/05/triplink-overview-scaled.jpg'),(336,100,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:7:{s:5:\"width\";i:1810;s:6:\"height\";i:2560;s:4:\"file\";s:36:\"2024/05/triplink-overview-scaled.jpg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:630447;s:5:\"sizes\";a:8:{s:6:\"medium\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"triplink-overview-212x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:212;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:20010;}s:5:\"large\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:30:\"triplink-overview-724x1024.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:724;s:6:\"height\";i:1024;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:151592;}s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"triplink-overview-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:8472;}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:30:\"triplink-overview-768x1086.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:1086;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:166281;}s:9:\"1536x1536\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"triplink-overview-1086x1536.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1086;s:6:\"height\";i:1536;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:292378;}s:9:\"2048x2048\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"triplink-overview-1448x2048.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1448;s:6:\"height\";i:2048;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:454494;}s:17:\"project_thumbnail\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"triplink-overview-424x600.jpg\