0)6 04 01 47 65'),(1629,391,'_phone','field_6627d850e71a2'),(1630,391,'contact_text','Do you have a question or a project? Don\'t hesitate to contact me using the form or the information below!'),(1631,391,'_contact_text','field_6627d85fe71a3'),(1632,391,'sub_title','Keep <strong>In touch</strong>'),(1633,391,'_sub_title','field_667844a74d523'),(1634,391,'required_field','Fields marked with <span class=\"field__text--red\">*</span> are required.'),(1635,391,'_required_field','field_66784559dd8ff'),(1639,392,'github_link','https://github.com/loicdelanoe/projet-cv-delanoe-loic-286'),(1640,392,'site_link','https://cv.loicdelanoe.com'),(1641,392,'resume','<h2>Summary</h2>\r\nThis was the first project I did during my second year of study. The aim was to create a really basic website using HTML, CSS and Javacript.\r\n<h3>Constraint</h3>\r\nWe had to create this site from an existing site, copy its design and then replace its content with our own so that the site looked like a CV.\r\n<h3>Inspiration</h3>\r\nI chose to redesign the <a href=\"https://monday-128.webflow.io/home-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Monday</a> site, which is a template from the Webflow site. The site was basic but my aim was to reproduce it as closely as possible and make it accessible without Javascript and for users with disabilities.'),(1642,392,'resume_image','93'),(1643,392,'overview_image','85'),(1644,392,'functionality','<h2>Features</h2>\r\n<h3>On scroll animation</h3>\r\nScroll animations add a touch of interactivity by bringing elements to life as soon as they enter the field of vision. This makes navigation more immersive and engaging.\r\n<h3>Responsive design</h3>\r\nMy responsive design ensures optimum accessibility on a variety of devices, including desktops, tablets and smartphones. So my visitors can enjoy the content seamlessly, whatever device they\'re using.\r\n<h3>Performance Optimisation</h3>\r\nI\'ve maximised the use of CSS functionality to reduce reliance on JavaScript. This improves site performance while offering a variety of visual effects and features that enrich the user experience.'),(1645,392,'other_image',''),(1646,392,'colors','#000000,#FFFFFF'),(1647,392,'gallery','253'),(1648,392,'_github_link','field_661e37eea2f99'),(1649,392,'_site_link','field_661e3822a2f9a'),(1650,392,'_resume','field_661e3843a2f9b'),(1651,392,'_resume_image','field_661e386ba2f9c'),(1652,392,'_overview_image','field_661e393da2f9f'),(1653,392,'_functionality','field_661e3953a2fa0'),(1654,392,'_other_image','field_661e3973a2fa1'),(1655,392,'_colors','field_6626134621eff'),(1656,392,'_gallery','field_66699a5c46ac9'),(1657,392,'_edit_last','1'),(1658,392,'_edit_lock','1719167073:1'),(1659,393,'github_link','https://github.com/loicdelanoe/nextjs-portfolio-v1'),(1660,393,'site_link','https://nextjs-portfolio-v1-kjhi.vercel.app/'),(1661,393,'resume','<h2>Summary</h2>\r\nThis site is the first version of a portfolio I created as a personal project to develop my skills in Javascript, Typescript, CSS and HTML. For this project I didn\'t create a design beforehand because the aim was to concentrate on the technical side. For the styling of the pages I used the <a href=\"https://tailwindcss.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">TailwindCSS</a> framework to save time and for the client side I used the <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">NextJS</a> framework, which offers a number of features.'),(1662,393,'resume_image','94'),(1663,393,'overview_image','86'),(1664,393,'functionality','<h2>Features</h2>\r\n<h3>NextJS Framework</h3>\r\nI used the NextJS framework for this site. I chose NextJS to discover development exclusively in Javascript, because it offers a system of ready-to-use and easy-to-use routes. To create a route, all you have to do is create a folder with the name of the route in the \"pages\" folder, launch the server and enter the corresponding URL.\r\n<h3>TailwindCSS</h3>\r\nIn addition to NextJS, I\'ve integrated TailwindCSS to style the pages. TailwindCSS lets you create elegant, responsive interfaces quickly thanks to its preconfigured utility classes.\r\n\r\nFor the contact form, I used the <a href=\"https://nodemailer.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Nodemailer</a> module to manage the sending of emails.'),(1665,393,'other_image',''),(1666,393,'colors','#FB923C,#181A1D,#EF4844'),(1667,393,'gallery','268,267'),(1668,393,'_github_link','field_661e37eea2f99'),(1669,393,'_site_link','field_661e3822a2f9a'),(1670,393,'_resume','field_661e3843a2f9b'),(1671,393,'_resume_image','field_661e386ba2f9c'),(1672,393,'_overview_image','field_661e393da2f9f'),(1673,393,'_functionality','field_661e3953a2fa0'),(1674,393,'_other_image','field_661e3973a2fa1'),(1675,393,'_colors','field_6626134621eff'),(1676,393,'_gallery','field_66699a5c46ac9'),(1677,393,'_edit_last','1'),(1678,393,'_edit_lock','1719167131:1'),(1679,394,'github_link','https://github.com/tecg-dwm/dwm-soundtrekker'),(1680,394,'site_link',''),(1681,394,'resume','<h2>Summary</h2>\r\nThis project was carried out as part of the Application Design course. We had to create an application that combined location discovery with music.\r\n<h3>Inspiration</h3>\r\nFor my design, I decided to take inspiration from <a href=\"https://totemus.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Totemus</a>, a treasure-hunting application that lets you discover many different places.\r\n<h3>Design</h3>\r\nFor the design, I decided to keep the style simple so that users don\'t get lost in the many different paths available.'),(1682,394,'resume_image','99'),(1683,394,'overview_image','100'),(1684,394,'functionality','<h2>Features</h2>\r\n<h3>Customization</h3>\r\nTriplink features a personalised experience when users sign up. They will be invited to choose the style of music they like, followed by a tutorial on how the application works so they don\'t get lost.\r\n<h3>Social</h3>\r\nTriplink has a social networking system where you can follow other users, in a similar way to Instagram. Users can also create collections of routes and group them together.\r\n<h3>Audio</h3>\r\nWhat\'s special about Triplink is that you can visit places while listening to related music, and the application also takes into account your choice of music.'),(1685,394,'colors','#F09D5D,#1B1A20,#FFFFFF,#F3F3F3'),(1686,394,'gallery','255,254'),(1687,394,'_github_link','field_661e37eea2f99'),(1688,394,'_site_link','field_661e3822a2f9a'),(1689,394,'_resume','field_661e3843a2f9b'),(1690,394,'_resume_image','field_661e386ba2f9c'),(1691,394,'_overview_image','field_661e393da2f9f'),(1692,394,'_functionality','field_661e3953a2fa0'),(1693,394,'_colors','field_6626134621eff'),(1694,394,'_gallery','field_66699a5c46ac9'),(1695,394,'_edit_last','1'),(1696,394,'_edit_lock','1719167179:1'),(1697,395,'github_link','https://github.com/loicdelanoe/sef'),(1698,395,'site_link','https://sef.loicdelanoe.com'),(1699,395,'resume','<h2>Summary</h2>\r\nThis project was carried out as part of the Web Design course. We had to create a site for the SEF Huy non-profit association to replace their old site.\r\n<h3>Inspiration</h3>\r\nFor the structure, I had to read up on the websites of associations that are similar to what SEF does. As for the colours, I chose one that evokes a \'zen attitude\' so as not to frighten users.'),(1700,395,'resume_image','102'),(1701,395,'overview_image','256'),(1702,395,'functionality','<h2>Features</h2>\r\n<h3>JavaScript</h3>\r\nThere is not much javascript for this website, so even without javascript the site is accessible:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>On scroll animation,</li>\r\n 	<li>Carousel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Contact form</h3>\r\nThis site features a contact form with back-end validation carried out by myself.'),(1703,395,'colors','#3C516F,#4F72A5,#E5EEF5,#F3F9FE,#F2F2F2'),(1704,395,'gallery','259,258,257'),(1705,395,'_github_link','field_661e37eea2f99'),(1706,395,'_site_link','field_661e3822a2f9a'),(1707,395,'_resume','field_661e3843a2f9b'),(1708,395,'_resume_image','field_661e386ba2f9c'),(1709,395,'_overview_image','field_661e393da2f9f'),(1710,395,'_functionality','field_661e3953a2fa0'),(1711,395,'_colors','field_6626134621eff'),(1712,395,'_gallery','field_66699a5c46ac9'),(1713,395,'_edit_last','1'),(1714,395,'_edit_lock','1719166255:1'),(1715,396,'github_link','https://github.com/loicdelanoe/portfolio-wordpress'),(1716,396,'site_link','https://loicdelanoe.com'),(1717,396,'resume','<h2>Summary</h2>\r\nThis project was carried out as part of the Web Design course. We had to create our own portfolio from A to Z, so that the site would best represent us.\r\n<h3>Guidelines</h3>\r\nThis website had to contain at least a home page, an \'about us\' page to introduce ourselves, a contact page with a form so that users could get in touch with us, a \'projects\' page where all the projects we have completed had to be listed, and an individual page for each project.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(1718,396,'resume_image','261'),(1719,396,'overview_image','262'),(1720,396,'functionality','<h2>Inspiration</h2>\r\nFor the layout, I wanted to make something clean and breathable so that the user wouldn\'t be lost with too much information on the page.\r\n\r\nIn terms of design, I chose a serif font for the titles, resembling a didone for elegance, Kalnia, I also chose this font for its teardrop-shaped endings, reminiscent of the musical notes on a score. For the second font, I opted for a geometric linear, Poppins, to add contrast with Kalnia.\r\n<h3>Technologies</h3>\r\nOn the front end I used HTML, SCSS and Javascript. The SCSS allowed me to separate my different style sheets during development so that I didn\'t get lost in a 3000-line style sheet. There are a few features in Javascript, such as :\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>scroll animation, using the <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Intersection_Observer_API\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Intersection Observer API;</a></li>\r\n 	<li>hover over project thumbnails and images;</li>\r\n 	<li>copy colours by clicking on a colour in a project.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOn the back-end, I used PHP with WordPress and developed my form validation system.'),(1721,396,'colors','#2C231E,#F0ECE6,#F8F7F5'),(1722,396,'gallery','266,265,264,263'),(1723,396,'_github_link','field_661e37eea2f99'),(1724,396,'_site_link','field_661e3822a2f9a'),(1725,396,'_resume','field_661e3843a2f9b'),(1726,396,'_resume_image','field_661e386ba2f9c'),(1727,396,'_overview_image','field_661e393da2f9f'),(1728,396,'_functionality','field_661e3953a2fa0'),(1729,396,'_colors','field_6626134621eff'),(1730,396,'_gallery','field_66699a5c46ac9'),(1731,396,'_edit_last','1'),(1732,396,'_edit_lock','1719167247:1'),(1733,397,'about_text','<h3>Mon parcours</h3>\r\nJe m\'appelle Loïc Delanoë, étudiant en deuxième année de bachelier en techniques infographiques, spécialité Web à la <a href=\"https://hepl.be/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HEPL</a>. Après une 1<sup>er</sup> année en licence d\'économie à <a href=\"https://www.univ-tours.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">l\'université de Tours</a>, j\'ai décidé de me réorienter afin de poursuivre mes études dans le domaine de ma passion, le design et la programmation.\r\n<h3>Ma vision</h3>\r\nPour moi un design doit rester tout autant efficace, qu\'il doit être esthétique, de plus au niveau web, il est aussi important pour moi que chaque site web soit accessible à tous.'),(1734,397,'_about_text','field_6627daa36e88c'),(1735,397,'profil_image','90'),(1736,397,'_profil_image','field_6627dabc6e88d'),(1737,397,'sub_title','À Propos <strong>De moi</strong>'),(1738,397,'_sub_title','field_6678054d7096a'),(1739,397,'formation_title','Mes <strong>Formations</strong>'),(1740,397,'_formation_title','field_66783513114d8'),(1741,397,'approach_title','Mon <strong>Approche</strong>'),(1742,397,'_approach_title','field_66783521114d9'),(1743,397,'test','test'),(1744,397,'_test','field_667836e00aa1a'),(1745,397,'gfrde','sdfghjk'),(1746,397,'_gfrde','field_66781d50899f8'),(1747,397,'studies_title',''),(1748,397,'_studies_title','field_66783513114d8'),(1749,397,'first_title','Design'),(1750,397,'_first_title','field_66783f6a9970e'),(1751,397,'first_content','Il est important de fournir un design complet et soigné aux clients afin qu’ils aient une bonne idée de ce que leur site va donner quand il sera déployé.'),(1752,397,'_first_content','field_66783f8d9970f'),(1753,397,'secondary_title','Développement'),(1754,397,'_secondary_title','field_66783faff8d3c'),(1755,397,'secondary_content','Après le design, le développement est tout aussi important, mais surtout le respect des normes / conventions des langages (sémantique en HTML).'),(1756,397,'_secondary_content','field_66783fbdf8d3d'),(1757,397,'third_title','Accessibilité'),(1758,397,'_third_title','field_66783fcdf8d3e'),(1759,397,'third_content','L’accessibilité d’un site web est cruciale, en effet n’importe quel site internet doit être pensé aussi pour les personnes en situation de handicap.'),(1760,397,'_third_content','field_66783fe7f8d3f'),(1761,398,'about_text','<h3>My journey</h3>\r\nMy name is Loïc Delanoë, and I\'m a student in the second year of a bachelor\'s degree in computer graphics techniques, specialising in the Web, at the <a href=\"https://www.hepl.be/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HEPL</a>. After a 1st year in economics at the <a href=\"https://www.univ-tours.fr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">University of Tours</a>, I decided to change direction to pursue my studies in the field of my passion, design and programming.\r\n<h3>My vision</h3>\r\nFor me, a design has to be just as effective as it is aesthetically pleasing. What\'s more, when it comes to the web, it\'s just as important for me that every website is accessible to everyone.'),(1762,398,'_about_text','field_6627daa36e88c'),(1763,398,'profil_image','90'),(1764,398,'_profil_image','field_6627dabc6e88d'),(1765,398,'sub_title','About <strong>Me</strong>'),(1766,398,'_sub_title','field_6678054d7096a'),(1767,398,'formation_title','My <strong>Studies</strong>'),(1768,398,'_formation_title','field_66783513114d8'),(1769,398,'approach_title','My <strong>Approach</strong>'),(1770,398,'_approach_title','field_66783521114d9'),(1771,398,'test','test'),(1772,398,'_test','field_667836e00aa1a'),(1773,398,'gfrde',''),(1774,398,'_gfrde','field_66781d50899f8'),(1775,398,'first_title','Design'),(1776,398,'_first_title','field_66783f6a9970e'),(1777,398,'first_content','It\'s important to provide clients with a complete, polished design so that they have a good idea of what their site will look like when it\'s deployed.'),(1778,398,'_first_content','field_66783f8d9970f'),(1779,398,'secondary_title','Development'),(1780,398,'_secondary_title','field_66783faff8d3c'),(1781,398,'secondary_content','After design, development is just as important, but above all compliance with the standards / conventions of the languages (semantics in HTML).'),(1782,398,'_secondary_content','field_66783fbdf8d3d'),(1783,398,'third_title','Accessibility'),(1784,398,'_third_title','field_66783fcdf8d3e'),(1785,398,'third_content','The accessibility of a website is crucial. In fact, any website must also be designed for people with disabilities.'),(1786,398,'_third_content','field_66783fe7f8d3f'),(1787,401,'_edit_last','1'),(1788,401,'_edit_lock','1721034543:1'),(1789,402,'_wp_attached_file','2024/07/thumbnail-lcdj-scaled.jpg'),(1790,402,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:7:{s:5:\"width\";i:2560;s:6:\"height\";i:2560;s:4:\"file\";s:33:\"2024/07/thumbnail-lcdj-scaled.jpg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:847618;s:5:\"sizes\";a:7:{s:6:\"medium\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:26:\"thumbnail-lcdj-600x600.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:600;s:6:\"height\";i:600;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:69958;}s:5:\"large\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"thumbnail-lcdj-1024x1024.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:1024;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:187960;}s:9:\"th