 web level, it is also important that each website is accessible to everyone.'),(1927,419,'_about_text','field_6627daa36e88c'),(1928,419,'profil_image','90'),(1929,419,'_profil_image','field_6627dabc6e88d'),(1930,419,'sub_title','About <strong>Me</strong>'),(1931,419,'_sub_title','field_6678054d7096a'),(1932,419,'formation_title','My <strong>Studies</strong>'),(1933,419,'_formation_title','field_66783513114d8'),(1934,419,'approach_title','My <strong>Approach</strong>'),(1935,419,'_approach_title','field_66783521114d9'),(1936,419,'test','test'),(1937,419,'_test','field_667836e00aa1a'),(1938,419,'gfrde',''),(1939,419,'_gfrde','field_66781d50899f8'),(1940,419,'first_title','Design'),(1941,419,'_first_title','field_66783f6a9970e'),(1942,419,'first_content','It\'s important to provide clients with a complete, polished design so that they have a good idea of what their site will look like when it\'s deployed.'),(1943,419,'_first_content','field_66783f8d9970f'),(1944,419,'secondary_title','Development'),(1945,419,'_secondary_title','field_66783faff8d3c'),(1946,419,'secondary_content','After design, development is just as important, but above all compliance with the standards / conventions of the languages (semantics in HTML).'),(1947,419,'_secondary_content','field_66783fbdf8d3d'),(1948,419,'third_title','Accessibility'),(1949,419,'_third_title','field_66783fcdf8d3e'),(1950,419,'third_content','The accessibility of a website is crucial. In fact, any website must also be designed for people with disabilities.'),(1951,419,'_third_content','field_66783fe7f8d3f'),(1952,421,'_edit_last','1'),(1953,421,'_edit_lock','1726766810:1'),(1954,422,'_wp_attached_file','2024/09/sdla-thumbnail.jpg'),(1955,422,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";i:1294;s:6:\"height\";i:1294;s:4:\"file\";s:26:\"2024/09/sdla-thumbnail.jpg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:606775;s:5:\"sizes\";a:5:{s:6:\"medium\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:26:\"sdla-thumbnail-600x600.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:600;s:6:\"height\";i:600;s:9:\