age, je suis resté sur quelque chose de simple et lisible avec une police sans serif, Poppins. Pour les couleurs, j\'ai repris celle de la commune afin de garder une cohérence.\r\n<h3>Technologies</h3>\r\nAfin de pouvoir fournir le site dans les temps, j\'ai utilisé WordPress le CMS le plus connu. Pour ce site je n\'ai pas utilisé de JavaScript, j\'ai utilisé exclusivement du HTML et du SCSS.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(1978,421,'_functionality','field_661e3953a2fa0'),(1979,421,'colors','#870727,#1A0D10,#FFFFFF'),(1980,421,'_colors','field_6626134621eff'),(1981,421,'gallery','426,424'),(1982,421,'_gallery','field_66699a5c46ac9'),(1983,427,'github_link','https://github.com/loicdelanoe/Saint-Laurent-d-Aigouze'),(1984,427,'site_link','https://saint-laurent-daigouze.yellowpublicite.fr/rue-du-phare'),(1985,427,'resume','<h2>Summary</h2>\r\n<strong>(En)quête de PATRIMOINE: déambulations dans les rues de Saint-Laurent d\'Aigouze</strong> is a website telling the story of each street in <a href=\"https://www.ville-saint-laurent-daigouze.fr/\">Saint-Laurent d\'Aigouze</a>. There are 15 streets on the site, each page containing their history, the various panels and a number of useful links. This project was carried out in cooperation with <a href=\"https://yellowpublicite.fr/\">Yellow Publicité</a>, who were responsible for producing the panels.\r\n<h3>Client requirements</h3>\r\nThe client wanted a simple design with a section to show the old signs as well as the new signs featuring the Provençal name of each street. The page had to include a section telling the story of the street and at the end some useful links.'),(1986,427,'resume_image','422'),(1987,427,'overview_image','423'),(1988,427,'functionality','<h2>Inspiration</h2>\r\nFor inspiration, Yellow publicité provided me with a visual that I used as a basis for the final design. For the layout, I stuck to something simple and legible with a sans serif font, Poppins. As for the colours, I used those of the municipality in order to maintain consistency.\r\n<h3>Technologies</h3>\r\nIn order to deliver the site on time, I used WordPress, the best-known CMS. For this site I didn\'t use JavaScript, I used HTML and SCSS exclusively.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(1989,427,'colors','#870727,#1A0D10,#FFFFFF'),(1990,427,'gallery','426,424'),(1991,427,'_github_link','field_661e37eea2f99'),(1992,427,'_site_link','field_661e3822a2f9a'),(1993,427,'_resume','field_661e3843a2f9b'),(1994,427,'_resume_image','field_661e386ba2f9c'),(1995,427,'_overview_image','field_661e393da2f9f'),(1996,427,'_functionality','field_661e3953a2fa0'),(1997,427,'_colors','field_6626134621eff'),(1998,427,'_gallery','field_66699a5c46ac9'),(1999,427,'_edit_last','1'),(2000,427,'_edit_lock','1725979829:1'),(2001,430,'title','Loïc Delanoë Développeur Web'),(2002,430,'_title','field_665ae75a90534'),(2003,430,'name','Loïc Delanoë'),(2004,430,'_name','field_665ae82a957fc'),(2005,430,'job','Dev Full-stack'),(2006,430,'_job','field_665ae835957fd'),(2007,430,'projects_title','Derniers <strong>Projets</strong>'),(2008,430,'_projects_title','field_667773d72f254'),(2009,431,'title','Loïc Delanoë Développeur Web'),(2010,431,'_title','field_665ae75a90534'),(2011,431,'name','Loïc Delanoë'),(2012,431,'_name','field_665ae82a957fc'),(2013,431,'job','Full-stack Dev'),(2014,431,'_job','field_665ae835957fd'),(2015,431,'projects_title','Last <strong>Projects</strong>'),(2016,431,'_projects_title','field_667773d72f254'),(2017,440,'_edit_last','1'),(2018,440,'_edit_lock','1737730186:1');
